Optimal Solutions:

class Solution(object):
    def isPalindrome(self, s):
        """
        :type s: str
        :rtype: bool
        """
        s = ''.join(ans.lower() for ans in s if ans.isalnum())
        left = 0
        right = len(s) - 1 

        while left < right:
            if s[left] != s[right]:
                return False
            left += 1
            right -= 1

        return True
================================================================================================
 
import re
class Solution(object):
    def isPalindrome(self, s):
        """
        :type s: str
        :rtype: bool
        """
        s = re.sub('[^a-zA-Z0-9]', '', s) .lower()
        return s == s[::-1] 
================================================================================================

Complexity
Time complexity: O(n)
Space complexity: O(n)

